properties.Name: MinorityCategory
properties.Description:
A minority category that may be defined or identified with a legal entity party.

Ex:
- Certified Small Disadvantaged Business 
- SBA Certified HUBZone Business 
- SBA Certified 8(a) Program Participant 
- DoT Certified Disadvantaged Business Enterprise - Black Owned
- Community Developed Corporation  
- Labor Surplus Area Firm  
- Alaskan Native Corporation Owned Firm  
- Native Hawaiian Organization Owned Firm  
- American Indian Owned  
- Service Disabled Veteran Owned 
- Woman Owned
